"title": "5824: cruelty, examples of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5824: cruelty, examples of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture condemns cruelty, and gives examples of situations in which it was practised.</p>\n<h2>Cruelty is an expression of wickedness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:4\">PSA 71:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:28-Rom1:31\">ROM 1:28–1:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:16\">PSA 35:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:14\">PSA 86:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:5\">PRO 17:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:1\">ECC 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:12\">AMO 5:12</a></p>\n<h2>Forms of cruelty</h2>\n<h3>The cruel nature of war</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:12\">2KI 8:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:16\">2KI 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:15\">ISA 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:18\">ISA 13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:14\">HOS 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:16\">HOS 13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:10\">NAM 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>The cruel nature of rape</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:2\">GEN 34:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:25\">JDG 19:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:14\">2SA 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:2\">ZEC 14:2</a></p>\n<h3>The cruel nature of words</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:1-Job17:2\">JOB 17:1–17:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:10\">PSA 42:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:31\">MRK 15:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:6-1Sam1:7\">1SA 1:6–1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:3\">JOB 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:7\">PSA 22:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:11\">PSA 35:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:50-Ps89:51\">PSA 89:50–89:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:8\">PSA 102:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:7\">JER 20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:14\">LAM 3:14</a></p>\n<h2>Particular examples of cruelty</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:23-Gen37:24\">GEN 37:23–37:24</a> <em>Joseph's brothers</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:5-Gen49:7\">GEN 49:5–49:7</a> <em>Simeon and Levi</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:22\">EXO 1:22</a> <em>Pharaoh</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:6\">JDG 1:6</a> <em>Judah's cruelty to a local king</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:2-Judg4:3\">JDG 4:2–4:3</a> <em>Sisera</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:6-Judg10:8\">JDG 10:6–10:8</a> <em>the Philistines and Ammonites</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:10\">2CH 16:10</a> <em>Asa</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:8-Prov5:9\">PRO 5:8–5:9</a> <em>the adulteress</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:7\">JER 21:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:13-Dan3:20\">DAN 3:13–3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:15\">JER 37:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6-Jer38:7\">JER 38:6–38:7</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:29\">EZK 22:29</a> <em>Israel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:18-Nah3:19\">NAM 3:18–3:19</a> <em>the king of Assyria</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:16\">MAT 2:16</a> <em>King Herod</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:26-Matt27:31\">MAT 27:26–27:31</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:15-Mark15:20\">MRK 15:15–15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:15\">JHN 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:33-Luke23:39\">LUK 23:33–23:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:35-Matt27:44\">MAT 27:35–27:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:24-Mark15:32\">MRK 15:24–15:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:18\">JHN 19:18</a></p>",
